created via kubectl\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md:\n  Line 13: Sandbox 创建处理器负责处理 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 和 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 请求，将用户的 AgentRuntime 或 CodeInterpreter 定义转化为实际的 Sandbox（或 SandboxClaim）Kubernetes 资源，等待其进入 running 状态，解析 Pod IP 和入口点，持久化到 Store，并返回包含 sessionId 的响应。\n  Line 23:       → handleAgentRuntimeCreate / handleCodeInterpreterCreate\n  Line 25:         → 2. 从 Informer 缓存获取 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter\n  Line 38: - **client-go typed client**: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` 提供 `AgentRuntimeInterface` 和 `CodeInterpreterInterface`，用于读取 workload 模板定义\n  Line 39: - **client-go informers**: `SharedInformerFactory` → `Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes()` / `CodeInterpreters()` 提供本地缓存\n  Line 40: - **client-go listers**: `AgentRuntimeLister` / `CodeInterpreterLister` 用于只读查询\n  Line 51:     → AgentRuntime / CodeInterpreter\n  Line 71:     Kind      string `json:\"kind\"`      // \"AgentRuntime\" 或 \"CodeInterpreter\"\n  Line 77: // - Kind 必须为 AgentRuntime 或 CodeInterpreter\n  Line 130:     \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",    // 可选，handler 会覆盖\n  Line 161: | 404 | Informer 缓存中找不到 AgentRuntime | `{\"message\":\"agent runtime not found\"}` |\n  Line 167: 与 AgentRuntime 端点结构相同，区别在于：\n  Line 169: 1. Kind 固定为 `CodeInterpreter`\n  Line 170: 2. CodeInterpreter 支持 `WarmPoolSize > 0` 时创建 SandboxClaim 而非完整 Sandbox\n  Line 171: 3. CodeInterpreter 支持 `AuthMode`（`picod` 或 `none`），影响是否注入 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量\n  Line 183: handleAgentRuntimeCreate(c *gin.Context):\n  Line 186:   3. sandboxReq.Kind = types.AgentRuntimeKind  // 强制覆盖\n  Line 193: getAgentRuntime(namespace, name):\n  Line 194:   1. informerFactory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Lister().\n  Line 195:        AgentRuntimes(namespace).Get(name)\n  Line 196:   2. 若返回 k8s errors.IsNotFound → 返回 ErrAgentRuntimeNotFound\n  Line 198:   4. 返回 *runtimev1al