{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775838870248,"sessionID":"ses_287c20b03ffelPJGdxrKY95Lwa","part":{"id":"prt_d783ebae6001kApxAUU8HJwxZZ","messageID":"msg_d783eaffa001T5DyJiODh4MVRq","sessionID":"ses_287c20b03ffelPJGdxrKY95Lwa","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838915708,"sessionID":"ses_287c20b03ffelPJGdxrKY95Lwa","part":{"id":"prt_d783ec6a80017opkD2wqS045Tr","messageID":"msg_d783eaffa001T5DyJiODh4MVRq","sessionID":"ses_287c20b03ffelPJGdxrKY95Lwa","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_e696f1ba5c014172a1693f49","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Delta Spec: AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRD type definitions in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-001\n- **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Base Spec**: `deployment/client-go.md` (client-go library types)\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: AgentRuntime Type Definition\n\n### AR-001-001: AgentRuntime type with required spec fields\n\n- **GIVEN** a Go package at `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** defining `AgentRuntime` struct with kubebuilder markers\n- **THEN** the type SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n- **AND** SHALL include `Spec` field of type `AgentRuntimeSpec`\n- **AND** SHALL include `Status` field of type `AgentRuntimeStatus`\n\n### AR-001-002: AgentRuntimeSpec required fields\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct definition\n- **WHEN** defining the spec fields\n- **THEN** `MaxSessionDuration` SHALL be `string` type, required, default `\"8h\"`\n- **AND** `SessionTimeout` SHALL be `string` type, required, default `\"15m\"`\n- **AND** `TargetPort` SHALL be `[]TargetPort` type, required, non-empty\n\n### AR-001-003: AgentRuntime optional podTemplate\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeSpec` definition\n- **WHEN** `podTemplate` field is specified\n- **THEN** it SHALL be of type `PodTemplateSpec` (custom, not corev1.PodTemplateSpec)\n- **AND** SHALL be optional (omitempty)\n\n### AR-001-004: AgentRuntimeStatus with conditions\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct definition\n- **WHEN** defining status subresource\n- **THEN** it SHALL include `Conditions` of type `[]metav1.Condition`\n- **AND** SHALL include `ObservedGeneration` of type `int64`\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: CodeInterpreter Type Definition\n\n### AR-001-005: CodeInterpreter type definition\n\n- **GIVEN** a Go package at `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** defining `CodeInterpreter` struct with kubebuilder markers\n- **THEN** the type SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n- **AND** SHALL include `Spec` field of type `CodeInterpreterSpec`\n- **AND** SHALL include `Status` field of type `CodeInterpreterStatus`\n\n### AR-001-006: CodeInterpreterSpec fields\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct definition\n- **WHEN** defining spec fields\n- **THEN** `AuthMode` SHALL be of type `AuthMode` (enum: \"picod\", \"none\"), optional, default `\"picod\"`\n- **AND** `MaxSessionDuration` SHALL be `string` type, optional, default `\"8h\"`\n- **AND** `SessionTimeout` SHALL be `string` type, optional, default `\"15m\"`\n- **AND** `Ports` SHALL be `[]TargetPort` type, optional\n- **AND** `Template` SHALL be of type `ContainerTemplateSpec`, required\n- **AND** `WarmPoolSize` SHALL be `int32` type, optional, default `0`\n\n### AR-001-007: CodeInterpreterStatus with ready field\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct definition\n- **WHEN** defining status subresource\n- **THEN** it SHALL include `Conditions` of type `[]metav1.Condition`\n- **AND** SHALL include `ObservedGeneration` of type `int64`\n- **AND** SHALL include `Ready` of type `bool`\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Shared Type Definitions\n\n### AR-001-008: TargetPort type\n\n- **GIVEN** shared type definitions in `types.go`\n- **WHEN** defining `TargetPort` struct\n- **THEN** it SHALL include `Port` of type `int32`, required\n- **AND** SHALL include `Protocol` of type `string` (HTTP/HTTPS)\n- **AND** SHALL include `Name` of type `string`, optional\n- **AND** SHALL include `PathPrefix` of type `string`, optional\n\n### AR-001-009: PodTemplateSpec type\n\n- **GIVEN** shared type definitions in `types.go`\n- **WHEN** defining `PodTemplateSpec` struct\n- **THEN** it SHALL include `metav1.ObjectMeta` for metadata\n- **AND** SHALL include `Spec` field of type `PodSpec` (selective fields from corev1.PodSpec)\n\n### AR-001-010: ContainerTemplateSpec type\n\n- **GIVEN** shared type definitions in `types.go`\n- **WHEN** defining `ContainerTemplateSpec` struct\n- **THEN** it SHALL include `Image` of type `string`, required\n- **AND** SHALL include `Command` of type `[]string`, optional\n- **AND** SHALL include `Args` of type `[]string`, optional\n- **AND** SHALL include `Env` of type `[]corev1.EnvVar`, optional\n- **AND** SHALL include `Resources` of type `corev1.ResourceRequirements`, optional\n- **AND** SHALL include `RuntimeClassName` of type `*string`, optional\n\n### AR-001-011: AuthMode enum\n\n- **GIVEN** type definitions in `types.go`\n- **WHEN** defining `AuthMode` type\n- **THEN** it SHALL be a string type with kubebuilder validation: `enum:picod,enum:none`\n- **AND** default value SHALL be `\"picod\"`\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Scheme Registration\n\n### AR-001-012: Register types to scheme\n\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package\n- **WHEN** creating `register.go`\n- **THEN** it SHALL define `SchemeGroupVersion` as `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n- **AND** SHALL provide `addKnownTypes` function to register `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterList`\n- **AND** SHALL implement `AddToScheme` function for scheme registration\n\n### AR-001-013: Package documentation\n\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package\n- **WHEN** creating `doc.go`\n- **THEN** it SHALL include package-level kubebuilder markers: `// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, `// +versionName=v1alpha1`\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: DeepCopy Generation\n\n### AR-001-014: DeepCopy methods generation\n\n- **GIVEN** Go types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n- **WHEN** running `make generate` (controller-gen)\n- **THEN** `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** SHALL include `DeepCopyInto`, `DeepCopy` methods for `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterList`\n- **AND** SHALL include DeepCopy methods for all nested types: `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, `CodeInterpreterSpec`, `CodeInterpreterStatus`, `TargetPort`, `PodTemplateSpec`, `ContainerTemplateSpec`\n\n### AR-001-015: DeepCopy for lists\n\n- **GIVEN** list types in `types.go`\n- **WHEN** running controller-gen\n- **THEN** `AgentRuntimeList.DeepCopy()` SHALL return a copy with `Items` slice properly copied\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterList.DeepCopy()` SHALL return a copy with `Items` slice properly copied\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: CRD Generation\n\n### AR-001-016: CRD YAML generation for AgentRuntime\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentRuntime` type with kubebuilder markers\n- **WHEN** running `make gen-crd`\n- **THEN** CRD YAML SHALL be generated in `manifests/charts/base/crds/`\n- **AND** SHALL have `name: agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- **AND** SHALL have `spec.scope: Namespaced`\n- **AND** SHALL have `spec.versions[].name: v1alpha1`\n\n### AR-001-017: CRD YAML generation for CodeInterpreter\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreter` type with kubebuilder markers\n- **WHEN** running `make gen-crd`\n- **THEN** CRD YAML SHALL be generated in `manifests/charts/base/crds/`\n- **AND** SHALL have `name: codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- **AND** SHALL have `spec.scope: Namespaced`\n- **AND** SHALL have `spec.versions[].name: v1alpha1`\n\n### AR-001-018: CRD validation schema\n\n- **GIVEN** kubebuilder markers on type fields\n- **WHEN** generating CRD YAML\n- **THEN** validation rules SHALL be generated in OpenAPI v3 schema\n- **AND** `AgentRuntime.spec.maxSessionDuration` SHALL have validation (required, default \"8h\")\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreter.spec.authMode` SHALL have enum validation (picod, none)\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Client-go Compatibility\n\n### AR-001-019: Type name compatibility with client-go\n\n- **GIVEN** Go types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** running `make gen-client`\n- **THEN** client-go SHALL be generated without type name conflicts\n- **AND** generated client SHALL expect `AgentRuntime` type (not `AgentRuntimeSpec` or other)\n- **AND** generated client SHALL expect `CodeInterpreter` type\n\n### AR-001-020: List type compatibility\n\n- **GIVEN** Go types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** running `make gen-client`\n- **THEN** `AgentRuntimeList` SHALL have `Items` field of type `[]AgentRuntime`\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterList` SHALL have `Items` field of type `[]CodeInterpreter`\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Build Verification\n\n### AR-001-021: Go build succeeds\n\n- **GIVEN** complete type definitions in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** running `go build ./pkg/apis/...`\n- **THEN** compilation SHALL succeed without errors\n- **AND** all types SHALL be properly importable\n\n### AR-001-022: kubectl CRD apply\n\n- **GIVEN** generated CRD YAML files\n- **WHEN** applying to Kubernetes cluster with `kubectl apply -f`\n- **THEN** AgentRuntime CRD SHALL be created successfully\n- **AND** CodeInterpreter CRD SHALL be created successfully\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Base spec: `deployment/client-go.md`\n- Design: `proposal.md`\n- API Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- Version: `v1alpha1`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-001/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-001/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-001/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775838915696,"end":1775838915705}}}}
